 # Changelog
 
+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S5-P03-T065 (citation support/counter/mention evidence + graph; NOT_DEPLOYED)
+
+- Sixty-fifth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (closes S5-P03). Aligns the evidence/relationship benefit of Scite/ResearchRabbit/Litmaps: for each citation, capture the citation CONTEXT and label it support/counter/mention -- but the label is derived ONLY from explicit cue phrases found IN THAT CONTEXT, never from the citing paper's title or a model's impression. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a read-only library with NO model call, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/citation_evidence.py: classify_citation (takes ONLY the context; assigns support/counter/mention from the earliest cue found in the context, byte-exact located; no cue -> mention, never guessed; ASCII cues match on word boundaries so 'unlike' does not match inside 'unlikely'), build_citation_graph (feeds only the context to the classifier; citing_title is stored display-only, never classified), query_graph, and label_has_viewable_context. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S5-P03-T065/: citation_evidence_report.json, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S5-P03-T065/test-results/citation_evidence_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): every one of the 6 labels is backed by a cue byte-exact in its context (quote == context[offset:offset+length]); the label is not from the title -- classify_citation takes only the context, two conflict cases whose titles read as support (English 'supports and confirms' and Chinese 一致) are labeled counter because the context contradicts, a supportive-titled no-cue citation is labeled mention, and a naive title-based classifier disagrees on 5 cases; cue precision holds ('unlikely' is not counter, 'inconsistent with' stays counter, a genuine 'unlike ' is counter, the stem 'corroborate' is support); and the graph keeps support and counter edges to the same cited paper distinct. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S5-P03-T064 (Research Set / filtering / structured comparison; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Sixty-fourth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S5-P03). Aligns the research-set benefit of Elicit/Consensus: collect papers into a Research Set, extract structured method/sample/result fields, and compare them side by side -- WITHOUT guessing. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a read-only library, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/research_set.py: extract_fields (label/statistic-driven method/sample/result extraction where every value is a BYTE-EXACT span of the source with an evidence locator offset+length+quote, and a field with no marker is reported {value:None, status:'missing'} -- 缺失不猜, never fabricated), make_set (a Research Set collection, deterministic order), comparison_table (per-paper rows x method/sample/result columns, each cell value+evidence or a missing flag), filter_set (reproducible has-field / keyword filtering, deterministic order), and traces_to_source (every non-missing value is byte-exact at its recorded source offset). Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S5-P03-T064/: research_set_report.json, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S5-P03-T064/test-results/research_set_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): every one of the 10 present Golden-Set fields traces byte-for-byte back to its source span (value == text[offset:offset+length], quote == value) and matches the hand label; all 5 intentionally-absent fields are reported missing with no fabricated value; a hallucinated value and a guess-a-default extractor are BOTH rejected by the traceability check (so the 回原文 guarantee is non-vacuous); and has-field filtering is identical across 3 runs, deterministically ordered and a non-trivial subset (P001/P002/P005), while a keyword filter yields a different set (P001/P003). Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
